answers.body_markdown:
      $table-&gt;unsignedBigInteger(&#39;anynameyouwant_id&#39;);
      $table-&gt;foreign(&#39;anynameyouwant_id&#39;)-&gt;references(&#39;id&#39;)-&gt;on(&#39;which table you want to refer&#39;);

this is the basic concept of the foreign key in laravel.
